{"tid":2406342,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"50辣車放煙花狂飆 當警無到","createTime":"2021-02-13T06:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T06:30:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"330e0560ad4c3aa9f9abc943dc22b3f65280da50","tid":2406342,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:24:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210213/GGBFCMZ5TJD7LDXMA5FV7NDMGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210213%2FGGBFCMZ5TJD7LDXMA5FV7NDMGE%2F&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=245d0c53\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210213%2FGGBFCMZ5TJD7LDXMA5FV7NDMGE%2F&h=a0f96b1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210213/GGBFCMZ5TJD7LDXMA5FV7NDMGE/</a><br />\n<br />\n50辣車放煙花狂飆 當警無到<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】飆車黨非法賽車賀歲，網上流傳多條短片，昨大年初一凌晨，50部辣車突襲火炭路，如「攞正牌」一樣，燃爆煙花作「起步禮」，辣車應聲開跑，其間衝燈及瘋狂左穿右插狂飆，途中亦再爆煙花，遇見警車仍視若無睹，繼續飛馳。警方表示，已掌握部份涉案私家車車牌號碼及資料，不排除採取檢控行動。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：民間「煙花滙」炮仗聲四起<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MvWq5D3Zsh7jTgkOca-NT36DUc0=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E2MNREKBBRHDDCVKHRYDP3U2YI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMvWq5D3Zsh7jTgkOca-NT36DUc0%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE2MNREKBBRHDDCVKHRYDP3U2YI.jpg&h=f0a18f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■多部辣車以放煙花作「起步禮」，狂飆途中亦有燃放。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警稱已掌握部份資料<br />\n<br />\n網上片段所見，現場在火炭路近松頭下路交界，黃格前四條行車線排滿約50部車輛，不乏辣車如本田TYPE R、本田S2000、福士GTI等。其中一段片標示時間為凌晨2時4分，一枚煙花爆破後，引擎聲四起，車隊不理燈號高速飛馳。附近的車輛司機赫見車隊來勢洶洶，慌忙避開，沿途陸續有煙花燃放，儼如澳門大賽車，拍片者亦忍不住說：「嘩，黐晒線。」<br />\n<br />\n另一片段顯示，辣車駛經火炭路山尾街交界時，遇見警車亮着藍燈停在十字路口位，但車隊視作透明，並沒減速或停下，一路衝燈飆前，警車之後追截。片段可見，車隊駛出九龍後，沿龍翔道再往沙田方行駛，繼續爭先恐後飛馳，即使有危險品車輛在旁，也切線爬頭。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Sl1IXrTt5TmMhU6rLPFqMURVjko=/638x300/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O5C5KWT6BNBQ3J6UWXSRZYGFOQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSl1IXrTt5TmMhU6rLPFqMURVjko%3D%2F638x300%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO5C5KWT6BNBQ3J6UWXSRZYGFOQ.gif&h=057b580b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■車隊無視警車（箭嘴示）衝燈，警車其後追截。"},{"pid":"ea34bdd9ddccf88bb3e12b700c6a0e39b1d1a4d4","tid":2406342,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:25:39.000Z","msg":"成班都有錢既夠撚膽拉人咩  拉學生就話姐"},{"pid":"784fdf7ba1de82ab44319e669148bda4e6a4564c","tid":2406342,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:30:45.000Z","msg":"車仔貼光時，即刻出解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}